Class StataDateDisplayFormats

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.paces.Stata.Utilities.StataDateDisplayFormats

  • public class StataDateDisplayFormats
extends Object
    Static methods used to translate date values into standard formatted date/datetime strings based on Stata conventions Also need to implement small parser to handle the translation from Stata datetime formats to the Java equivalents where possible.

    0.0.0
